songs.title: Bankroll
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Lil Mosey]
Ooh, ooh
Ayy, ooh, ooh
Ooh

Gucci socks, my pants fall
I bust down my ankle, see you fuck niggas from my angle
Doubled up my bankroll
Gucci socks, my pants fall

I bust down my ankle, see you fuck niggas from my angle
Doubled up my bankroll

Turn money to pesos, goin' somewhere you can't go
She do what I say so, In the 'Rari I race ho
I do what I want, I buy what I want
Bitch, you need some gum
Today I brought out my gun
Moaning

[Chorus: Lil Mosey]
